Description:Firebending Lesson (SVar:X:Count$Kicked.5.2) deals 5 damage when kicked ({4} additional cost) and 2 damage when not kicked. P0 controls 6 lands and holds Firebending Lesson. P1 controls a 6/4 Craw Wurm — survives 2 damage but dies from 5. The AI should pay kicker (has sufficient mana), dealing 5 damage. Before the wave-5 fix, Count$Kicked.5.2 always evaluated to 2 (unkicked) even when kicker was paid, leaving the 6/4 alive.

